# create my own data cycle
1. plan- layout plan to conduct research
2. collection- collecting data that can be used for analyzing
3. processing- Taking the stored data and having the system process the information
4. visualization - make graphs or any visual to showcase data
5. storing- saving data for further research
6. analysis- interpreting what the data means through the visualization of graphs
